00:36:40,011 --> 00:36:40,846
Sound familiar?

634
00:36:42,548 --> 00:36:43,582
- Can I have a smoke?

635
00:36:54,595 --> 00:36:56,530
- Where's your brother?

636
00:36:57,765 --> 00:36:58,900
- Somewhere in Ireland.

637
00:37:00,402 --> 00:37:01,837
- Oh.

638
00:37:01,837 --> 00:37:02,804
You like games.

639
00:37:05,842 --> 00:37:10,581
Gerard Anthony Fallon, born in 1957, Belfast,

640
00:37:10,581 --> 00:37:12,883
first arrested for assaulting a British

641
00:37:12,883 --> 00:37:14,418
army officer in 1972.

642
00:37:15,953 --> 00:37:18,523
Received scholarship to Trinity College, Dublin,

643
00:37:18,523 --> 00:37:20,792
