653
00:37:43,018 --> 00:37:44,286
Cut from throat to dick.

654
00:37:45,154 --> 00:37:46,456
- What are you saying?

655
00:37:46,456 --> 00:37:48,525
- If you want Liam, I'll give him to you.

656
00:37:49,959 --> 00:37:51,594
But not in here.

657
00:37:51,594 --> 00:37:53,063
- You think I'm gonna get you out of here?

658
00:37:53,063 --> 00:37:53,898
You're crazy.

659
00:37:55,032 --> 00:37:56,534
I came a long way.

660
00:37:56,534 --> 00:37:59,371
