661
00:37:59,371 --> 00:38:02,073
- Can't have much cooperation behind six feet of stone.

662
00:38:05,311 --> 00:38:06,112
Clock's ticking.

663
00:38:13,086 --> 00:38:14,421
- Sergeant. - Yes, sir.

664
00:38:19,727 --> 00:38:20,728
- Beautiful country.

665
00:38:21,930 --> 00:38:23,899
But all it takes is one look at people like you

