00:38:23,899 --> 00:38:26,135
to know why my grandparents left.

667
00:38:26,135 --> 00:38:28,003
- Appreciate the vote of confidence.

668
00:38:28,003 --> 00:38:29,039
- Where to, first?

669
00:38:30,173 --> 00:38:31,675
- A fellow called Brian Fagen.

670
00:38:33,076 --> 00:38:34,545
- Yeah, what about him?

671
00:38:34,545 --> 00:38:36,113
- He's a good man.

672
00:38:36,113 --> 00:38:38,416
Probably only friend I have left.

673
00:38:38,416 --> 00:38:41,019
- You want to drop the anonymous tip before your trial?

674
00:38:41,019 --> 00:38:42,554
- What tip was that?

675
00:38:42,554 --> 00:38:44,890
- That Liam's the one that blew up the Liden family.

676
00:38:46,125 --> 00:38:46,960
And my sister.

677
00:38:47,894 --> 00:38:49,162
- Don't know about that.

678
00:38:51,497 --> 00:38:52,333
- So was it you?

679
00:38:53,267 --> 00:38:54,902
- I never said push the button.

680
00:38:54,902 --> 00:38:56,670
- Well, if you weren't responsible,

681
00:38:57,838 --> 00:38:58,974
then why didn't you say something?

