00:39:53,604 --> 00:39:54,838
- [John] Excuse me, miss?

687
00:39:56,006 --> 00:39:57,908
Is there a Brian Fagen living here?

688
00:39:59,010 --> 00:40:00,512
- No. - Do you know what happened

689
00:40:00,512 --> 00:40:01,346
