690
00:40:14,494 --> 00:40:17,165
So, you married George Bailey.

691
00:40:17,165 --> 00:40:18,499
Good lad.

692
00:40:18,499 --> 00:40:19,467
When's he due back?

693
00:40:21,002 --> 00:40:23,639
- George has been dead going on three years now, Gerry.

694
00:40:24,707 --> 00:40:26,008
- Christ, Mary, I'm sorry.

695
00:40:27,409 --> 00:40:30,613
- RUC picked him up one night coming back from the club.

696
