00:40:46,666 --> 00:40:48,968
- That's why we're here, Mary.

704
00:40:48,968 --> 00:40:49,869
We need to see Brian.

705
00:40:50,870 --> 00:40:52,072
- Haven't seen him.

706
00:40:52,072 --> 00:40:53,173
Not since the incident with Liam.

707
00:40:53,173 --> 00:40:53,941
No one has.

708
00:40:55,142 --> 00:40:56,844
He'll stay under for a while, I'm guessing.

709
00:40:59,280 --> 00:41:00,782
- Who could put the word out, we need to see him.

710
00:41:00,782 --> 00:41:02,650
- Mommy, Mommy, look what I did at school today.

711
00:41:04,687 --> 00:41:05,621
- Oh, it's lovely.

712
00:41:08,724 --> 00:41:09,558
Lucy.

713
00:41:10,594 --> 00:41:12,562
This is Mr. Farrel.

714
00:41:12,562 --> 00:41:13,964
He's an old friend of your Uncle Brian.

715
00:41:13,964 --> 00:41:14,965
- Hello.

716
00:41:14,965 --> 00:41:16,334
Are you a bad man?

