00:41:55,913 --> 00:41:59,150
- Liam could smell a Brit spy like a ripe fart.

730
00:42:00,785 --> 00:42:02,420
- Not this one he won't.

731
00:42:06,392 --> 00:42:08,561
(honking)

732
00:42:09,996 --> 00:42:12,299
- Tonight, come to the Raiden.

