00:42:21,876 --> 00:42:22,878
- Sounds good, Mitt.

736
00:42:33,389 --> 00:42:34,725
- So, pick a bunk.

737
00:42:34,725 --> 00:42:36,961
It ain't the Ritz, but it's functional.

738
00:42:36,961 --> 00:42:39,497
- Can I caution you again, my friend?

