00:42:40,832 --> 00:42:42,367
- I'm quite aware of that.

741
00:42:42,367 --> 00:42:44,603
- You think people don't know they're moving stuff in here?

742
00:42:44,603 --> 00:42:47,273
Your man is about as subtle as a bull in a china shop.

743
00:42:48,241 --> 00:42:49,775
- Are you testing me?

744
00:42:49,775 --> 00:42:52,179
- I'm saying if you want Liam, you've got to live like him.

745
00:42:52,179 --> 00:42:54,147
Underground, on the streets.

746
00:42:54,147 --> 00:42:56,350
You got to get inside his head.

747
00:42:56,350 --> 00:42:57,751
Think Irish.

748
00:42:57,751 --> 00:42:58,820
Feel our pain.

749
00:42:59,921 --> 00:43:00,722
- Is that right?

