758
00:43:25,183 --> 00:43:26,084
I know that pain.

759
00:43:27,452 --> 00:43:29,322
I've lived in the streets and I've been poor.

760
00:43:29,322 --> 00:43:31,391
But it will never be an excuse for pulling

761
00:43:31,391 --> 00:43:34,495
the maniacal, sick shit that you've pulled.

