765
00:43:49,211 --> 00:43:50,046
Brothers.

766
00:43:56,653 --> 00:43:58,823
And now, they want us to lie down again,

767
00:43:58,823 --> 00:44:01,259
like good wee kitties, and declare a cease fire.

768
00:44:02,327 --> 00:44:05,097
Because they say so? - Hell no.

