784
00:45:09,873 --> 00:45:11,308
O'Brien, Plantis.

785
00:45:13,076 --> 00:45:16,180
What do you know about explosives?

786
00:45:16,180 --> 00:45:17,381
- Not much.

787
00:45:19,050 --> 00:45:20,484
- Ever fired a gun before?

788
00:45:20,484 --> 00:45:21,753
- Sure.

